description: Describes your OpsWorks CM account attributes. This operation is synchronous.

nested_items.name: Attributes
nested_items.description: The attributes that are currently set for the account.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The attribute name. The following are supported attribute names.
ServerLimit: The number of current servers/maximum number of servers allowed. By default, you can have a maximum of 10 servers.
ManualBackupLimit: The number of current manual backups/maximum number of backups allowed. By default, you can have a maximum of 50 manual backups saved.

nested_items.name: Used
nested_items.description: The current usage, such as the current number of servers that are associated with the account.
